                        <p>Brodhead: So now we’re done, may I ask you a question?</p>
<p>Moderator: No.</p>
<p><em>Monday Monday had originally planned this as a festive column in which a giant vengeful roast turkey rampages through Duke, killing everyone.</em></p>
